{"tid":1768350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(美國佬又搞事)伊朗控國內動亂「美國幹的」 索賠1300億美元","createTime":"2019-12-04T04:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T05:09:02.000Z","uid":40267,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1226371e053e2d608632ecb374dfbde3df04335f","tid":1768350,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"伊朗司法部指控，美國等西方大國組織伊朗國內的反政府示威，要求美國就<br />\n    伊朗國內動亂造成的損失給予1300億美元的賠償。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國對伊朗祭出經濟制裁，衝擊伊朗經濟，2週前伊<br />\n    朗政府突然宣佈將汽油價格上調50%，引發大規模群眾示威。伊朗司法部3日<br />\n    宣稱，美國等西方大國組織伊朗國內的反政府示威，要求美國就伊朗國內動<br />\n    亂造成的損失賠償1300億美元。<br />\n<br />\n    綜合外媒報導，伊朗當局指責美國等西方大國組織蔓延伊朗各地的反政府示<br />\n    威，伊朗司法部發言人埃斯邁里（Gholam Hossein Esmayeeli）3日宣稱，因<br />\n    為「美國的所作所為」造成直接損失，伊朗公民向法院提起訴訟和申訴，迄<br />\n    今為止，已提交超過360宗針對美國政府的民事訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n    伊朗司法部稱，根據<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">伊朗法院判決</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，美國須支付1300億美元的罰款，賠償因<br />\n    美國的罪行而對普通伊朗原告造成的損失，這些原告因白宮的單邊政策和白<br />\n    宮在伊朗國內動亂中的破壞性作用而遭受損失。"},{"pid":"a2bc33772e422cb27eed36d782eba3bdc6831867","tid":1768350,"uid":321374,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"攞1300億黎打柒你"},{"pid":"951145a82f8801c54c349dc83107f9ec9e44007a","tid":1768350,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17c8892101a65ef1306821132757f71bb1d7309c","tid":1768350,"uid":254788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:19:01.000Z","msg":"唔賠你咬美帝呀<br />\n痴撚線"},{"pid":"75b6791b213e6f81ef1a6ec5e050e934aae9a7b2","tid":1768350,"uid":40267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a2bc33772e422cb27eed36d782eba3bdc6831867","tid":1768350,"uid":321374,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"攞1300億黎打柒你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"1300支飛彈要唔要"},{"pid":"187360f51815a3152e8ab2db509efe839453ec1b","tid":1768350,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:21:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">日程表</span></span></strong><br />\n－－－－－－<strong><em>和理非合法活動集合</em></strong>－－－－－－</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期五 12 &middot; 6 </span><br />\n「吸吸可危」抵禦催淚彈集會</strong></span><br />\n- 19:00 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1766230/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1766230/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 12 &middot; 7</span><br />\n聲援被無理禁錮印尼手足</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1767815/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1767815/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 12 &middot; 8</span><br />\n國際人權日遊行</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 維園＞遮打道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1765090/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1765090/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n詳情參閱：<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=4216f1e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">眾籌要人！</span></span></strong><br />\n－－－－－－<strong><em>現時<span style=\"color: red;\">未達標</span>眾籌集合</em></strong>－－－－－－</div><br />\n英國戰線：推動英國版人權法、BNO平權、遊說國會<br />\n詳情：<